<#
.SYNOPSIS

Camera access from the lock screen must be disabled.

.NOTES
    Author          : Tibon Acha
    LinkedIn        : www.linkedin.com/in/tibon-a-8372a3227
    GitHub          : https://github.com/Tacha8
    Date Created    : 2025-08-11
    Last Modified   : 2024-08-11
